l, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1010430, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Peace be upon you [all], O saints of Allah! Peace be upon you, O arguments of Allah! Peace be upon you, O light of Allah in the darkness of the earth! Peace be upon you. Blessings of Allah be upon you and upon your Household, the pure and immaculate. May Allah accept my father and mother as ransoms for you! Indeed, you worshipped Allah sincerely and strove for His sake with due strife until death came upon you. So, may Allah curse all your enemies from the jinn and human beings. And I release myself before Allah and before you from them (i.e. your enemies).", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Salaam ho aap par ay auliya’e Khuda. Salaam ho aap par ay (zameen’e Khuda par) Allah ki hujjat. Salaam ho aap par ay zameen ki taarikiyo’n (andhero’n) mein Allah ke noor. Salaam ho aap par Allah ka durood ho aap par aur aap ke paak o paakeeza ghar waalo’n par. Mere maa baap aap par fida o qurbaan ho jaaye aap ne Allah ki mukhlisaana ibaadat ki aur raahe Khuda mein jihad karte huwe haq’e jehaad adaa kar diya yahan tak-keh jame shahadat nosh kiya. Jinn o ins mein se aap ke tamaam dushmano par Khuda laanat kare keh mai bargah'e rububiyat mein aur aap ki bargah mein un sabse bezaar hu.", "Urdu": "آپ پر سلام ہو اے اولیاء خدا! آپ پر سلام ہو جو خدا کی دلیل و حجت ہیں! آپ پر سلام ہو جو زمین کی تاریکیوں میں خدا کا نور ہیں! آپ پر سلام ہو خدا کی رحمتیں ہوں آپ پر اور آپ کے پاک و پاکیزہ اہل بیتؑ پر، آپ پر میرے ماں باپ قربان! آپ نے مخلصانہ طور پر خدا کی عبادت کی اور خدا کی راہ میں جہاد کیا جس طرح جہاد کرنے کا حق ہے حتیٰ کہ آپ کی موت آگئی پس خدا لعنت کرے آپ کے تمام دشمنوں پر جو جنوں اور انسانوں میں سے ہیں میں آپ کے اور خدا کے سامنے ان سے برائت کرتا ہوں۔", "RArabic": "ASSALAAMO A’LAYKUM YAA AWLEYAAA-AL LAAHE ASSALAAMO A’LAYKUM YAA HOJAJAL LAAHE ASSALAAMO A’LAYKUM YAA NOORAL LAAHE FEE ZOLOMAATIL ARZE ASSALAAMO A’LAYKUM SALAWAATUL LAAHE A’LAYKUM WA A’LAA AALE BAYTEKOMUT TAYYEBEENAT TAAHEREENA BE ABEE ANTUM WA UMMEE LAQAD A’BADTOMUL LAAHA MUKHLESEENA WA JAAHAD-TUM FIL LAAHE HAQQA JEHAADEHEE HATTAA ATAAKOMUL YAQEENO FA LA-A’NAL LAAHO AA’DAAA-AKUM MENAL JINNE WAL INSE AJMA-E’EN WA ANAA ABRA-O ELAL LAAHE WA ELAYKUM MINHUM.", "ArabicText1": "اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْکُمْ یَااَوْلِیَآئَ اللہِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْکُمْ یَاحُجَجَ اللہِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْکُمْ یَانُوْرَ اللہِ فِیْ ظُلُمَاتِ الْاَرْضِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْکُمْ صَلَوَاتُ اللہِ عَلَیْکُمْ وَعَلٰی آلِ بَیْتِکُمُ الطَّیِّبِیْنَ الطَّاھِرِیْنَ بِاَبِیْ اَنْتُمْ وَاُمِّیْ لَقَدْ عَبَدْتُمُ اللہَ مُخْلِصِیْنَ وَجَاْھَدْتُمْ فِی اللہِ حَقَّ جِھَادِہٖ حَتّٰی اَتَاکُمُ الْیَقِیْنُ فَلَعَنَ اللہُ اَعْدَٓاْئَکُمْ مِنَ الْجِنِّ وَالْاِنْسِ اَجْمَعِیْنَ وَاَنَا اَبْرَئُ اِلٰی اللہِ وَاِلَیْکُمْ مِنْھُمْ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1010150, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O my master, O Aba Ibrahim, Musa, the son of Ja`far! O my master, O Abal Hasan, Ali, the son of Musa! O my master, O Aba-Ja`far, Muhammad, the son of Ali! O my master, O Abal Hasan, Ali, the son of Muhammad! I am your servant, I believe in your secret and open affairs, and I am staying with you as your guest, on this day, which is Wednesday, and I am in your vicinity; so, receive me as your guest and neighbor, [I ask you] by your Household, the pure and immaculate.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay mere maula Abu Ibrahim Moosa bin Jafar (a.s), ay mere aqaa ay Abul Hasan Ali bin Moosa (a.s), ay mere aqaa ay Abu Jafar Muhammad bin Ali (a.s), ay mere aqaa ay Abul Hasan Ali bin Muhammad (a.s) mai aap sab hazraat ka ghulam hu. Mai aap ke baatin o zaahir par imaan rakhta hu, mai aaj ke din roze Chaar-Shamba (Wednesday) jo keh aap ka din hai aap ka mehmaan hu aur aap hazraat ki panah ka khast-gaar hu. Pas aap hazraat meri mehmaan nawazi farmaaye aur panah de aap ko aap ke paak o paakeeza ghar waalo’n ka waasta.", "Urdu": "اے میرے سردار اے ابوابراہیم موسیٰ کاظم ؑ ابن جعفر صادقؑ اے میرے سردار اے ابو الحسنؑ علی رضاؑ ابن موسٰی کاظمؑ!اے میرے سردار اے ابو جعفر محمد تقیؑ ابن علی رضاؑ اے میرے سردار اے ابوالحسنؑ علی نقیؑ ابن محمد تقیؑ! میں آپ سب کا غلام ہوں آپ کے باطن و ظاہر پر ایمان رکھتا ہوں یہ آپ کا دن ہے میں اس میں آپ کا مہمان ہوں۔ یہ بدھ کا دن ہے اور آپ کی پناہ میں ہوں اب میری مہمان نوازی کیجیے اور مجھے پناہ دیجیے۔ آپ کو آپ کے پاک و پاکیزہ خاندان کاواسطہ دیتا ہوں۔", "RArabic": "YAA MAWLAAYA YAA ABAA IBRAAHEEMA MOOSABNA JAA’FAR YAA MAWLAAYA YAA ABAL HASANE A’LIY YABNA MOOSAA YAA MAWLAAYA YAA ABAA JA’FARE MOHAMMAD ABNA A’LIYYE YAA MAWLAAYA YAA ABAL HASANE A’LIY YABNA MOHAMMADIN ANAA MAWLAN LAKUM MOMENUN BE SIRREKUM WA JAHREKUM MOTAZAY YEFUN BEKUM FEE YAWMEKUM HAAZAA WA HOWA YAWMUL ARBA-A’A-E WA MUSTAJEERUN BEKUM FA AZEEFOONEE WA AJEEROONEE BE AALE BAYTEKOMUT TAYYEBEENAT TAAHEREENA.", "ArabicText1": "یَامَوْلَایَ یَااَبَا اِبْرَاْھِیْمَ مُوْسَی ابْنَ جَعْفَرٍ یَامَوْلَایَ یَااَبَا الْحَسَنِ عَلِیَّ بْنَ مُوْسٰی یَامَوْلَایَ یَااَبَا جَعْفَرٍ مُحَمَّدَ بْنَ عَلِیٍّ یَامَوْلَایَ یَا اَبَا الْحَسَنِ عَلِیَّ بْنَ مُحَمَّدٍ اَنَا مَوْلًی لَّکُمْ مُؤْمِنٌ بِسِرِّکُمْ وَجَھْرِکُمْ مُتَضَیِّفٌ بِکُمْ فِیْ یَوْمِکُمْ ھٰذَا وَھُوَ یَوْمُ الْاَرْبِعَآئِ وَمُسْتَجِیْرٌۢ بِکُمْ فَاَضِیْفُوْنِیْ وَاَجِیْرُوْنِیْ بِآلِ بَیْتِکُمُ الطَّیِّبِیْنَ الطَّاھِرِیْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlue